<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Verifikasi Tanda Tangan — Inspira Mailer</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/Group 1597880519.png">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

/* ── ANIMATED BACKGROUND ── */
body {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 32px 16px;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  position: relative;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  background: #060f2e;
}

/* Gradient mesh that shifts */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 20% 30%, rgba(26,86,168,.55) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 80% 70%, rgba(15,50,112,.6) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 80% at 50% 10%, rgba(7,24,64,.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
  animation: bgShift 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  z-index: 0;
}

@keyframes bgShift {
  0%   { background-position: 0% 0%, 100% 100%, 50% 0%; }
  50%  {
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 60% 50%, rgba(26,86,168,.5) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 20% 80%, rgba(15,50,112,.55) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 80% at 80% 20%, rgba(7,24,64,.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  100% {
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 80% 20%, rgba(26,86,168,.5) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 10% 60%, rgba(15,50,112,.5) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 80% at 50% 90%, rgba(7,24,64,.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
}

/* Floating orbs */
.orb {
  position: fixed;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(60px);
  opacity: .25;
  z-index: 0;
  animation: floatOrb linear infinite;
}
.orb-1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: #1a56a8; top: -100px; left: -100px; animation-duration: 20s; }
.orb-2 { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: #0f3270; bottom: -80px; right: -80px; animation-duration: 16s; animation-delay: -5s; }
.orb-3 { width: 250px; height: 250px; background: #2e6abf; top: 40%; left: 60%; animation-duration: 24s; animation-delay: -10s; }

@keyframes floatOrb {
  0%,100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
  25%      { transform: translate(30px, -40px) scale(1.05); }
  50%      { transform: translate(-20px, 30px) scale(.95); }
  75%      { transform: translate(40px, 20px) scale(1.03); }
}

/* Grid dot overlay */
body::after {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 32px 32px;
  z-index: 0;
}

/* ── CARD ── */
.card {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 460px;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 24px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow:
    0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.08),
    0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2),
    0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
}

/* ── HEADER VALID ── */
.header-valid {
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #071840 0%, #0f3270 55%, #1a56a8 100%);
  padding: 40px 28px 52px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.header-valid::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,.08) 0%, transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 85% 80%, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 0%, transparent 45%);
}
.header-valid::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 36px;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0 / 100% 100% 0 0;
}

/* ── HEADER INVALID ── */
.header-invalid {
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a0a0a 0%, #7f1d1d 55%, #c0392b 100%);
  padding: 40px 28px 52px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.header-invalid::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,.07) 0%, transparent 45%);
}
.header-invalid::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 36px;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0 / 100% 100% 0 0;
}

.badge-ring {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  width: 68px; height: 68px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 20px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
}

.header-eyebrow {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.header-title {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff; letter-spacing: -.3px; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.header-sub {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.65);
}

/* ── BODY ── */
.body { padding: 8px 28px 28px; }

.signer {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  padding: 20px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.signer-av {
  width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3270, #1a56a8);
  color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0; letter-spacing: -1px;
}
.signer-name { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.signer-sub  { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }

/* Info rows */
.info-list { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.info-row {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  padding: 12px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f7fa;
}
.info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.info-dot {
  width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 5px;
}
.dot-amber { background: #f59e0b; }
.dot-blue  { background: #3b82f6; }
.dot-red   { background: #ef4444; }
.info-label {
  font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
  color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.info-value { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: #111827; line-height: 1.4; }
.info-sub   { font-size: 11.5px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 2px; }
.info-sub a { color: #1a56a8; text-decoration: none; }

/* Scan badge */
.scan-badge {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: #f0f5ff;
  border: 1px solid #c7d9f5;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  font-size: 13px; color: #374151;
}
.scan-dot {
  width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: #1a56a8;
  animation: blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
@keyframes blink { 0%,100% { opacity:1; } 50% { opacity:.2; } }

/* Stamp */
.stamp {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  background: #f0f5ff;
  border: 1px solid #bfcfed;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
}
.stamp-icon {
  width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3270, #1a56a8);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.stamp-text { font-size: 13px; color: #1e3a6e; line-height: 1.5; }

/* Invalid */
.invalid-box {
  margin: 8px 0 0;
  background: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #fecaca;
  border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 20px; text-align: center;
}
.invalid-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #991b1b; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.invalid-desc  { font-size: 13px; color: #7f1d1d; line-height: 1.6; }

/* Footer */
.footer {
  padding: 14px 28px 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid #f5f5f5;
  text-align: center;
}
.footer-brand {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.footer-logo { width: 15px; height: 15px; object-fit: contain; opacity: .35; }
.footer-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #9ca3af; }
.footer-note { font-size: 11px; color: #c4c9d4; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Animated orbs -->
<div class="orb orb-1"></div>
<div class="orb orb-2"></div>
<div class="orb orb-3"></div>

<div class="card">

<%
if (valid && sig) {
  const d     = new Date(sig.signedAt);
  const sd    = scanTime;
  const M     = ['Januari','Februari','Maret','April','Mei','Juni','Juli','Agustus','September','Oktober','November','Desember'];
  const p     = n => String(n).padStart(2,'0');
  const fdt   = dt => `${dt.getDate()} ${M[dt.getMonth()]} ${dt.getFullYear()}, ${p(dt.getHours())}.${p(dt.getMinutes())}.${p(dt.getSeconds())}`;
  const inits = sig.fullName.split(' ').slice(0,2).map(w => w[0]).join('').toUpperCase();
%>

  <div class="header-valid">
    <div class="badge-ring">
      <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none">
        <path d="M7 15l6 6 10-10" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="header-eyebrow">Verifikasi Berhasil</div>
    <div class="header-title">Dokumen Sah &amp; Terverifikasi</div>
    <div class="header-sub">Tanda tangan digital ini valid dan dapat dipercaya</div>
  </div>

  <div class="body">

    <div class="signer">
      <div class="signer-av"><%= inits %></div>
      <div>
        <div class="signer-name"><%= sig.fullName %></div>
        <div class="signer-sub">
          <% if (sig.position && sig.organization) { %><%= sig.position %> &middot; <%= sig.organization %>
          <% } else { %><%= sig.position || sig.organization || '' %><% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-list">
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-dot dot-amber"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="info-label">Waktu Penandatanganan</div>
          <div class="info-value"><%= fdt(d) %> WIB</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% if (sig.location && (sig.location.label || sig.location.lat)) { %>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-dot dot-red"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="info-label">Lokasi</div>
          <div class="info-value"><%= sig.location.label || 'Tidak diketahui' %></div>
          <% if (sig.location.lat && sig.location.lng) { %>
          <div class="info-sub">
            <%= sig.location.lat.toFixed(5) %>, <%= sig.location.lng.toFixed(5) %>
            &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=<%= sig.location.lat %>,<%= sig.location.lng %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lihat peta</a>
          </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="scan-badge">
      <div class="scan-dot"></div>
      <span>Dipindai pada <%= fdt(sd) %> WIB</span>
    </div>

    <div class="stamp">
      <div class="stamp-icon">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
          <path d="M4 10l3.5 3.5 8-8" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="stamp-text">
        Dokumen ini <strong>SAH</strong> dan telah ditandatangani secara digital melalui <strong>Inspira Mailer</strong>.
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

<% } else { %>

  <div class="header-invalid">
    <div class="badge-ring">
      <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none">
        <path d="M8 8l14 14M22 8L8 22" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="header-eyebrow">Verifikasi Gagal</div>
    <div class="header-title">Dokumen Tidak Valid</div>
    <div class="header-sub">QR Code ini tidak dapat diverifikasi</div>
  </div>

  <div class="body">
    <div class="invalid-box">
      <div class="invalid-title">QR Code Tidak Dikenali</div>
      <div class="invalid-desc">
        QR Code ini tidak valid, sudah dihapus, atau telah dimodifikasi.<br>
        Hubungi penerbit dokumen untuk konfirmasi.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<% } %>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <img src="/img/Group 1597880519.png" class="footer-logo" alt="">
      <span class="footer-name">Inspira Mailer</span>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-note">Jangan percaya dokumen yang QR-nya tidak terverifikasi</div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
